name: Fibreglass Zoom Feather Flag
description:
• Feather flags are a great way of promoting your business on busy main roads, high streets and also trade shows. The use of vibrant colours and snappy slogans entice customers and make them pay attention to whatever you may want to sell.Â 
  • Feather flags can come in a choice of feather or tear drop shapes and are available in a variety of sizes. After being printed, the products come in an easy to assemble kit that is simple for the customer to put together. The use of robust, strong aluminium frames means that the flags are durable and able to endure windy or inclement weather.Â 
  • Feather flag kits also come with handy carry bags so that they can be easily transported from place to place and set up as they are required. The flags also come with a variety of bases, facilitating the flags' assembly in any location.
  • Available in 3 shapes
  • Choose from 7 base options
  • Lightweight fibreglass pole
  • Available in 4 heights: 2.8m, 3.4m, 4.5m and 5.6m
  • Printed on 115gsm Knitted Polyester

name: Fibreglass Curve Feather Flag
description:
• Feather flags are a great way of promoting your business on busy main roads, high streets and also trade shows. The use of vibrant colours and snappy slogans entice customers and make them pay attention to whatever you may want to sell.Â 
  • Feather flags can come in a choice of feather or tear drop shapes and are available in a variety of sizes. After being printed, the products come in an easy to assemble kit that is simple for the customer to put together. The use of robust, strong aluminium frames means that the flags are durable and able to endure windy or inclement weather.Â 
  • Feather flag kits also come with handy carry bags so that they can be easily transported from place to place and set up as they are required. The flags also come with a variety of bases, facilitating the flags' assembly in any location.
  • Available in 3 shapes
  • Choose from 7 base options
  • Lightweight fibreglass pole
  • Available in 4 heights: 2.8m, 3.4m, 4.5m and 5.6m
  • Printed on 115gsm Knitted Polyester

name: Fibreglass Square Teardrop Flag
description:
• Buy your Fibreglass Tear drop flags from the leaders in the UK printing industry. Our range of flags is perfect for stands at sales conventions or trade shows, and we can print them with your own artwork or design them to your specifications complete with your own company colours and logo.
  • Tear drop shaped flags are a great marketing tool. Use them to identify your brand at an industry event or take then to an outdoor sporting event to draw attention to your sponsorship or support. Outdoor use adds an eye-catching fluttering to these free-standing flags.Â 
  • Fibreglass Tear drop flagsÂ and stand are simple to self-assemble and you can choose a base to suit your location from our extensive range. Each kits comes complete with a handy carry bag to help with transportation and storage. The frame poles are made from robust, 100% aluminium, ensuring your tear drop-shaped promotional flags are stable and long lasting.
  • Available in 3 shapes.
  • Choose from 7 base options
  • Reinforced yet lightweight aluminium pole
  • Available in 4 heights: 2.8m, 3.4m, 4.5m and 5.6m
  • Printed on 115gsm Knitted Polyester

name: Fibreglass Drop Teardrop Flag
description:
• Buy your Fibreglass Tear drop flags from the leaders in the UK printing industry. Our range of flags is perfect for stands at sales conventions or trade shows, and we can print them with your own artwork or design them to your specifications complete with your own company colours and logo.
  • Tear drop shaped flags are a great marketing tool. Use them to identify your brand at an industry event or take then to an outdoor sporting event to draw attention to your sponsorship or support. Outdoor use adds an eye-catching fluttering to these free-standing flags.Â 
  • Fibreglass Tear drop flagsÂ and stand are simple to self-assemble and you can choose a base to suit your location from our extensive range. Each kits comes complete with a handy carry bag to help with transportation and storage. The frame poles are made from robust, 100% aluminium, ensuring your tear drop-shaped promotional flags are stable and long lasting.
  • Available in 3 shapes
  • Choose from 7 base options
  • Lightweight fibreglass pole
  • Available in 4 heights: 2.8m, 3.4m, 4.5m and 5.6m
  • Printed on 110gsm Knitted Polyester

name: Fibreglass Curve Teardrop Flag
description:
Teardrop flags are a great way of promoting your business on busy main roads, high streets and also trade shows. The use of vibrant colours and snappy slogans entice customers and make them pay attention to whatever you may want to sell.Â 

Teardrop flags can come in a choice of feather or tear drop shapes and are available in a variety of sizes. After being printed, the products come in an easy to assemble kit that is simple for the customer to put together. The use of robust, strong aluminium frames means that the flags are durable and able to endure windy or inclement weather.Â 
Teardrop flag kits also come with handy carry bags so that they can be easily transported from place to place and set up as they are required. The flags also come with a variety of bases, facilitating the flags' assembly in any location.
  • Available in 3 shapes
  • Choose from 7 base options
  • Lightweight fibreglass pole
  • Available in 4 heights: 2.8m, 3.4m, 4.5m and 5.6m
  • Printed on 115gsm Knitted Polyester
